Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in re-submission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR before a Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time to re-submit after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for all activities between first Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE and Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time before Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases where re-submission leads to approval
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR in successful re-submission cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in cases of multiple rejections
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to the next activity in the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR Cycle Time in the context of the entire process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER in cases that involve pre-approval after rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
